headline: Wall Street Remains Bullish on Carvana Co (CVNA)
summary: ​Carvana Co. (NYSE:CVNA) is one of the Best Revenue Growth Stocks to Invest In. Wall Street is bullish on Carvana Co. (NYSE:CVNA). On October 17, Marvin Fong from BTIG reiterated a Buy rating on the stock with a price target of $450. The analyst noted that he followed the company’s September ABS performance data closely […]
